snippet.title: Resident Evil Village - 4th Trailer
snippet.description:
How far would you go to save someone you love? After having everything taken from him, Ethan Winters is not only fighting for survival, but fighting to find his kidnapped daughter.
Resident Evil Village comes to PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox Series X|S, Xbox One, Steam, and Stadia on May 7th, 20201.
